    <comment>Hi,

I'd like to submit this package to Factory. 
It is an excellent and actively maintained source port of Doom, Heretic and Hexen games, with some unique features. This packages is split into 3 packages: international-doom, international-heretic, international-hexen, specifically so that users doing package searches on heretic and hexen can find it easily.

https://jnechaevsky.github.io/inter-doom/
https://github.com/JNechaevsky/international-doom
